{"tid":1243001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔應該再罷工!!","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:34:15.000Z","uid":219244,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"94237644ef7ccc2719894b2e3478b8a8bf5f96ce","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"我見有post講621 罷工罷課罷市<br />\n今次林鄭「暫緩」已經有啲中產願意收貨<br />\n再罷工未必達到效果<br />\n<br />\n加上罷工本身係好高成本嘅抗爭<br />\n近期已經就反送中發動咗<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兩</span>次</strong></span>罷工：分別係612(三)、617(一)<br />\n<br />\n罷工好處：<br />\n1)和平理性非暴力引起社會迴響<br />\n2)製造經濟壓力迫政府讓步<br />\n3)罷工嘅市民可以參與當日集會示威，人數多可以向政府施壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但</strong></span></span><br />\n大家試下從打工仔角度諗下：<br />\n1)上次難得老細同意罷工，好難講得出口要第二、三次罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2)上次冇話畀老細知純粹請病假，唔通今次又請病假?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3)上次放無薪假期罷工嘅話，已經承受經濟損失<br />\n<br />\n1and2會影響老細對打工仔嘅印象、3會有經濟損失<br />\n除非有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">工會組織</span></span></strong>，好多打工仔罷一次工已經係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好大付出</strong></span></span><br />\n更加多人因為唔同嘅理由唔會罷工(eg公務員or緊急服務、老細講明唔同意、有野要趕起)<br />\n<br />\n上兩次罷工事實上缺少大公司參與，未有對<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>經濟</strong></span>or<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">市民生活</span></strong>造成重大影響，效果唔係咁明顯<br />\n短期內連續發動效果唔明顯嘅罷工，除咗對參與罷工嘅市民製造<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無力感</strong></span><br />\n長遠仲會削弱罷工對政府嘅威懾力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下次再講罷工，政府只會覺得冇料到</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷工唔係唔得，但一定要好有組織*<br />\n要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一擊即中</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n連續多次無效嘅罷工只會犧牲參與罷工市民嘅民氣，而唔能夠達成目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好有組織* means起碼一個星期前聯絡各大有影響力嘅工會，務求對市面造成最大影響<br />\nand製造輿論令到市民有心理準備罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ynR8uYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynR8uYb.png&h=22adfd89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人意見only，歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc38b97fa957052f9eab9e866082c87a5179a41","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"push!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d9ca3b67671dbd86e79cd1300e06886135218b","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好似講得遲得滯，我見整晒文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但下次再發動罷工之前應該要諗清楚"},{"pid":"b9533a292f9d418201f7a9a0bc9a52796f0c6ecd","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e0d16115972e95abd5b49777f273ed4cab3d30","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b14b5c27cab821b107fded4496d5e78c9dea66","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68214a60097c774b308628df6cdd7b7b694b213c","tid":1243001,"uid":164987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84883163545f25e784720f48db138b4544d27cdc","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68214a60097c774b308628df6cdd7b7b694b213c","tid":1243001,"uid":164987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"Metoo"},{"pid":"923199603dff338d7a5d36bb45d41b5739cedb2b","tid":1243001,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"文宣戰我覺得做得好好，影響甚至大過罷工"},{"pid":"fb30439af0ca30087b7fabf0d6dd5a43d5918245","tid":1243001,"uid":193237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822d3b7dc54eab3cf8c41162e9965465963e588e","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84883163545f25e784720f48db138b4544d27cdc","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68214a60097c774b308628df6cdd7b7b694b213c","tid":1243001,"uid":164987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"Metoo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"大挪移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d974fb406bd043e0420a218a0cddd069aefe98b6","tid":1243001,"uid":199126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"真心，一個月三次，你叫我點請，勿吊，前兩次罷工有join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b141292a53375d07bd8fb82803d62a703a6bb631","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822d3b7dc54eab3cf8c41162e9965465963e588e","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84883163545f25e784720f48db138b4544d27cdc","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68214a60097c774b308628df6cdd7b7b694b213c","tid":1243001,"uid":164987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"Metoo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"大挪移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"爭少少認唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b6c6c9e74333dff0a6507f9be95ec72928f71a","tid":1243001,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"樓主講得岩<br />\n罷工其實要聯絡好多工會先"},{"pid":"f483cdfaefd1e2eb95d7a1718cc429256db63c51","tid":1243001,"uid":32647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"今次621完全睇唔到有人話跟罷<br />\n其實前兩次所謂罷工都係廢廢地，最多都係612 好多細鋪仔跟罷，但係講真對社會一d影響都無"},{"pid":"fadbf36ffbdac49c91b1c99fc0c2556052965c12","tid":1243001,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n上次都叫唔少小商戶響應<br />\n但始終都係冇核心既大集團參與<br />\n搞到罷左既作用都唔夠大<br />\n再搞會消耗民氣"},{"pid":"22bede9d9094961d4a8f1f5ffe49c48bf4392286","tid":1243001,"uid":193156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"三罷會唔會可以等到2 Jul<br />\n多啲時間去聯絡其他工會，方便打工仔請假<br />\n1 Jul 反正有遊行，遊行完休息一日好正常（我既心聲）<br />\n而家少左民陣帶頭威力細左（民陣支持同民陣發起有分別）"},{"pid":"1cdfee1a40b8645d532b69914713e2a1e06640ef","tid":1243001,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"啱 其實身邊都唔多人諗住罷"},{"pid":"c445590055742a72196dccb55d38b1840fa3fb0c","tid":1243001,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"請假又點叫罷工，所以話香港人都仲係有包袱<br />\n罷工都唔肯仲想改變D咩，台仔真係冇鬧錯，<br />\n你打工仔仲要幫老細諗埋，佢真係多尻謝你，<br />\n點解唔叫老細一齊出黎?<br />\n佢唔係香港人??係咪搞錯左D野呢個POST"},{"pid":"f2848b8d70af6b7967edd40853c5bbb0f5e93a1d","tid":1243001,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"冇可能做到一擊即中，只可以慢慢由少到多人罷"},{"pid":"88307d1fe1a744236ae7e0a39dfd70b2b32dab9c","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b141292a53375d07bd8fb82803d62a703a6bb631","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822d3b7dc54eab3cf8c41162e9965465963e588e","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84883163545f25e784720f48db138b4544d27cdc","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"Metoo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"大挪移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"爭少少認唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73777e9eb7ad7d1d56b15b2b3d011bd63a4c531","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c445590055742a72196dccb55d38b1840fa3fb0c","tid":1243001,"uid":162783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"請假又點叫罷工，所以話香港人都仲係有包袱<br />\n罷工都唔肯仲想改變D咩，台仔真係冇鬧錯，<br />\n你打工仔仲要幫老細諗埋，佢真係多尻謝你，<br />\n點解唔叫老細一齊出黎?<br />\n佢唔係香港人??係咪搞錯左D野呢個POST"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"我明白<br />\n問題係香港人未準備好罷工<br />\n<br />\n之前兩次罷工籌備都好<span style=\"color: red;\">倉猝</span><br />\n基本上都係得<span style=\"color: red;\">兩三日</span>時間準備，而且缺少重要工會or公司參與<br />\n<br />\n612係69遊行失敗之後<br />\n617最初係民陣係614話搞，但615林鄭宣布暫緩之後又話唔搞，跟住就出嚟澄清番話搞，成個過程好混亂<br />\n<br />\n所以兩次罷工出嚟效果都唔好<br />\n對於兩次罷工出嚟嘅人嚟講，佢哋已經罷左兩日工，但仍然未見成效<br />\n對於老闆嚟講，今次唔係純粹勞資糾紛，而係牽涉中港關係，支持罷工等於同中央作對，好少老細會願意得罪大陸<br />\n<br />\n我知自由理想係好好<br />\n但現實係大部份人都掛住搵食<br />\n要同老細講罷工本身就需要好大勇氣(仲要睇老細係咩人)<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要人支持罷工</span></span><br />\n就要諗下理想&amp;現實<br />\n知起碼call齊工會，廣發宣傳，製造到個氣氛係大家都會罷工，而且罷工係對政府有效施壓<br />\n咁樣大家先會支持罷工"},{"pid":"b7651a1a852629ed404c846ed59cd2fd550c62a1","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88307d1fe1a744236ae7e0a39dfd70b2b32dab9c","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b141292a53375d07bd8fb82803d62a703a6bb631","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822d3b7dc54eab3cf8c41162e9965465963e588e","tid":1243001,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"大挪移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"爭少少認唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9389841dc65a2f670e4c2b6b28e5d221f6ee93a7","tid":1243001,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:41:41.000Z","msg":"Hello<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621d3b9403beb6dd6ebbd82db542d8c1d6feb2ec","tid":1243001,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:43:34.000Z","msg":"有共識一齊罷先有效果"}]}